Title: Training Completed! Does Goku Have the Composure to Defeat Cell?!
Writer: Aya Matsui, Katsuyuki Sumizawa, Akira Toriyama
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Hiromi Tsuru
Plot: Goku and Gohan complete their training in the Hyperbolic Time Chamber, and fly down from The Lookout to greet their friends.
